Hey Guys!  Welcome to Disney Style!  This is your destination for Disney-inspired makeup and outfit tutorials, DIY projects, and all things Disney fashion. 

Watch Destination: Disney Style every Tuesday!  Featuring your faves LaurDIY, Meredith Foster, Jaleesa Moses and Lucy and Lydia.

Toy Reviews, DIY's, and Kid Videos Found Here! You can find kids make up challenge, mermaid video, toy reviews, and as seen on TV videos!
To tell you a little about the girls:  Isabella is 9 born 4/23 and Sydney is 6 born 11/12!  We are from Louisiana and while not at school Isabella loves playing Minecraft and Roblox.  Sydney is our gymnast and is on a gymnastics team at a local gym!  Please follow us on Instagram where we post pics of our dogs, cat, etc or on Twitter @realtoycritters.   Hope you enjoy watching our channel!!!

Fun diy-projects, crafts, experience the joy of doing it yourself! OFFICIAL CHANNEL.




For brand partnership enquires: brands@thesoul-publishing.com

NAME IT is inspired by kids – for kids. No matter how small or how big, how active or how lazy a day is in the lives of our children, NAME IT provides kids’ fashion for every occasion and every child. Through happy days, holidays and tough days of rain and mud, we offer our take on how to live a life inspired by kids. We create fun, affordable fashion for kids – always with an eye on what makes the grown up world of fashion tick.
